## Re-render Optimization

| Rule | Pattern |
|---|---|
| Derive state inline | `const fullName = first + ' ' + last` — never `useState` for computable values |
| Functional updates | `setItems(curr => [...curr, newItem])` when next state depends on current |
| Stable refs for transient values | `IntersectionObserver` instance, timer IDs → `useRef`, not `useState` |
| No components inside components | Define at module scope — inner definitions remount on every render |
| Narrow effect deps | `useEffect(() => track(userId), [userId])` not `[user]` |
| Ternary, never `&&` with falsy | `{count > 0 ? <Badge count={count} /> : null}` |

